
================================================================================
This is a plugin to interface the "librsb" sparse matrix library to Octave.
Author: Michele Martone
================================================================================

Build instructions:

sh autogen.sh
./configure
make
make check


Usage instructions:
# go in the directory where sparsersb.oct is located
octave
# you can use the sparsersb function

If you desire, you can pass some options to configure; e.g.: 
./configure CXXFLAGS="-O3  "
./configure CXXFLAGS="-O3  " LIBRSB_CONFIG=/opt/librsb-optimized/bin/librsb-config 

Developer notes:
 /usr/share/doc/octave3.2-htmldoc//interpreter/Getting-Started-with-Oct_002dFiles.html#Getting-Started-with-Oct_002dFiles
 http://octave.sourceforge.net/developers.html
================================================================================
